{"type": "article", "id": 16562, "title": "工具尺", "description": "", "date": "2015-10-26T06:50:59Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 79, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702125736Modq20juzFbcnUw9.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是把自带切割功能的尺子，它在常规的尺子下面加了一个底座，中间用弹簧转轴相连。而纸张就放在尺子和底座中间，再用弹簧调整纸它们的距离，就可以切割纸张了。这把尺子可以容纳6毫米的宽度，它实际代替了切割垫，不会伤到桌面，使用灵活，且非常节约空间。目前还没有售卖。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143754InqFCj5xDNpwkmhf.jpg\" width=\"650\" height=\"488\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75076923\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143755mfb9VhyvLiHatuCp.jpg\" width=\"650\" height=\"434\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66769231\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143755c0ujDISa4Kd1f7ZQ.jpg\" width=\"650\" height=\"488\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75076923\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143755IUrmbCugzKNSVYjh.jpg\" width=\"650\" height=\"430\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66153846\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}